summary: Yours truly went to the Good Omens premiere in London today and ... well, as a person who said beforehand it could either be...
body: Yours truly went to the Good Omens premiere in London today and … well, as a person who said beforehand it could either be really good or unfortunately not right, I am sold and excited. I cannot wait to see the rest of the series on Friday, I will definitely binge it. The heart and passion is there, in every single moment. What I have seen so far is promising enough to confine me to my room until I have seen it all. The preniere itself was … lovely, for the lack of a better word. Terry’s hat had its special spot in the first row. I hugged countless strangers as @neil-gaiman spoke about him, the great one. So many people tearing up, and I definitely wasn’t one of them. So, yeah…go watch Good Omens.
